text: Yara bara bara gonaha o aslilakarya theke bemce thake chotakhata aparadha karale'o niscaya apanara palanakartara ksama sudura bistrta. Tini tomadera samparke bhala janena, yakhana tini tomaderake srsti karechena mrttika theke ebam yakhana tomara matrgarbhe kaci sisu chile. Ata'eba tomara atnaprasansa karo na. Tini bhala janena ke sanyami.
